policy_language_erases_misconduct_record:
Police Union Contract:
Prevents certain disciplinary complaint or reports from being entered into the personnel file.
Section 22.11. To a transcribed copy of any notes made by a stenographer, or to any reports or complaints made by investigators or other persons, except those, which are deemed by the investigating agency to be confidential. No notes or reports, which are deemed to be confidential, may be entered in employee’s personnel file;
